#DominarRides | #NorthEastTour
 
Our riders went beyond the reel. And witnessed the real North-east.

The real lush foliage surrounding the long winding roads.

The real zen found only when one's in the heart of nature.

The real camaraderie that exists only between Dominar riders.

The real excitement of not holding back.
 
The ride ended, but the road continues ahead. The memories made on the road will forever stay with us.
 
Thank you North-East. Until we meet again.
 
Drop a ❤ in the comments below.
.
.

Starting Point: Guwahati

Head over to the link in the bio for more information!

#northeastindia #tourready #dominardiaries #dominar400 #dominar250 #d400 #d250 #rides #tour #touring

The all-new Dominar 400, factory fitted to tour, is the culmination of learnings across 6 successful odysseys, covering 144,100 KM, 5 continents, and 67 countries!

The latest upgraded accessories of Dominar 400 such as a Tall visor, Handguard, Engine bash plate, Leg guard, Carrier + Back stopper, Navigation stay, USB charging port, Saddle Stay – all make for a comfortable riding experience whether on the road or off it!

Watch the video as our Odyssey riders Candida Louis, Avinash P.S., Deepak Gupta aka Xtreme Moto Adventure, Sarath Shenoy, and Shilpa Balakrishnan are set out to test the Dominar 400 and its touring accessories.

latestIgtvVideos.caption:
From Vietnam, the riders take a coastal route, coursing through the countries of Cambodia, Thailand, Malaysia, Singapore and Sri Lanka. Several Indian motorbike flagbearers join the xBHP team, taking on the mantle of the third rider, as they make their way down south. Here’s the final chapter bringing this odyssey to close, but hopefully sparking a few more.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Dominar #RoofOfTheWorldOdyssey - North East Adventures
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Zero breakdowns. 3 Dominars. Six Riders. 17000 km. The bond of man and machine will be tested as the epic ride comes to an end. From the Traveller’s Paradise to ‘Adventure Pradesh’ to the last village of the North East, witness the unexplored Indian territories like never before. Discover why Dominar is the ultimate touring machine out there as its mettle is tested to the max while conquering the Great Himalayas. Catch the adventure and be a part of the journey with @sarath_shenoy , Ashish and @annyarun
